item.title: My server won't go online PI
item.dc:creator: @jailed jailed
item.description:
@jailed wrote:

It might be that most PI server listens to port 5555, and some listens to port 43594, you have to find out which port your server listens too and make sure your client connects to the same port, and that you have the port it listens to ‘forwarded’.
